<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Creative Technology.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Creative Technology.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Robertson, Stephens &amp; Co John Rossi raised his fiscal 1998 earnings estimate for Creative Technologies Inc to $2.35 a share from $2.25.</p>
<p>-- The company Monday reported a net profit for fiscal 1997 fourth quarter, ended June 30, of $0.55 a share versus a year earlier loss of $0.43 a share.</p>
<p>-- In a statement, Rossi said Creative repeated earlier rough guidance of sales growth at 10 to 15 pct, gross margin at about 30 pct and operating expenses of about 15 pct.</p>
<p>-- He called Creative &quot;one of the most undervalued franchises in technology.&quot;</p>
